{
  "nodes": [
    {
      "id": "57d423a6-b52e-43da-92a4-af7100d0b5a6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1055.0,
      "y": 1521.0,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "重点概念",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d7fafacd-1fd6-451b-969b-f67f9c34f0d0",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1475.0,
      "y": -10414.819444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "基础类型",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "6bf67bce-b02f-4102-8292-2e78a928908b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1895.0,
      "y": -16615.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Undefined",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "3bd26bc2-fbe9-46ea-89fd-e10e5db6079b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": -16815.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "定义",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "1815bea6-f3ea-4ac3-8773-35ec56c3df1c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -16815.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "表示的是一个变量不存在",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "6205ba28-17de-4d8d-a97c-7d6aa597acbd",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": -16415.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "常见的出现undefined的场景",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a60e8f84-2f62-49b0-9be9-ebb90b4332f7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -16655.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "使用只声明而未初始化的变量时",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "0890e8db-29fc-4326-9fb2-385c3070c7e0",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -16495.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "获取一个对象的某个不存在的属性（自身属性和原型链继承属性）时",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b42ee6a6-c42a-4f96-97a7-3abf52441efa",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -16335.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "函数没有明确的返回值时",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "dae4faba-17cf-4ea8-a4a7-ea68e54c0ac0",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -16175.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "函数定义时使用了多个形式参数（后文简称为形参），而在调用时传递的参数的数量少于形参数量",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "6035d7c6-ecf6-48d6-9959-0b6dc25e1216",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1895.0,
      "y": -15855.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Null",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "f5e61a72-732b-437e-b74c-e25db58c3132",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": -16015.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "定义",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "63580550-9118-4ca0-b306-c370db26528e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -16015.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "表示一个空指针对象",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b5cc2994-303b-4463-9cf2-d049a895821b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": -15695.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "常见的出现null的场景",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e028f729-ac8a-4556-b84b-2d51623ee7c7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -15855.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果声明的变量是为了以后保存某个值，则应该在声明时就将其赋值为“null”",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "59574626-d97b-436e-9c63-7a349b792ed9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -15695.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "获取DOM元素时，如果没有获取到指定的元素对象",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "aab728fb-f97e-4847-8d6d-dd1bafa1aa62",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -15535.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在使用正则表达式进行捕获时，如果没有捕获结果",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d889c1b8-2689-4a6c-b68f-8e1771c56481",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1895.0,
      "y": -14615.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Boolean",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "3c1ba630-4006-438e-803f-2c45d671044d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": -14615.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "不同类型与Boolean类型的值的转换",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "c8264960-1472-4956-b2a7-1732ab4af048",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -15295.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "String",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a29ff3e8-9096-446e-8251-51a784c799d5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -15375.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "空字符串\"\"或者''都会转换为false",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4548ef60-1ae2-48de-bfdd-c1e91891f789",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -15215.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "任何非空字符串都会转换为true，包括只有空格的字符串\" \"",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "0b7bdad3-1fff-4fa0-8b3d-ed61b23d76cf",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -14975.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Number",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d9293dbf-137e-4011-bc25-258fd1b4420b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -15055.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "0和NaN会转换为false",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "57c7c629-ce3b-48d9-a158-708b83485c84",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -14895.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "除了0和NaN以外，都会转换为true，包括表示无穷大和无穷小的Infinity和-Infinity",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "516a0ea9-4745-43fd-9063-5b68b42f1bac",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -14655.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Object",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "473fb40d-97be-4067-9ae6-37847a7a7a13",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -14735.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "当object为null时，会转换为false",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "fdaaf595-e0b0-4d36-abc8-42b2c8c1fb16",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -14575.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果object不为null，则都会转换为true，包括空对象{}",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "03da9864-9824-4eeb-b80f-fc948fe921a6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -14415.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Function",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "07fe9d12-5482-4e1f-9689-932f2a3cc803",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -14415.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "任何Function类型的值都会转换为true",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "ff82b1c2-5c1a-4968-a74e-8c7c3c5358ac",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -14255.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Null",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "0c933f0a-fa14-4f7b-88d9-0bfee7b6f2e3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -14255.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Null类型只有一个null值，会转换为false",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "ca4931b8-37bf-4c9d-8ea1-bc6a640ba931",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -14095.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Undefined",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "39eea1ab-e9c9-41e4-baea-1cd12951b328",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -14095.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Undefined类型只有一个undefined值，会转换为false",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "14f3689d-f88d-41fd-86de-1250f67e5b07",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1895.0,
      "y": -10113.652777777777,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Number",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "60d538f9-d44d-44e8-99ae-e59e63615e34",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": -13855.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "类型",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "46a38edb-9c27-47ac-bc1a-3c7f3766bffe",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -13935.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "整型数据",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "1fb34e2b-52bd-4b6a-8791-5d7fe716a508",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -13775.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "浮点型数据",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "63d6ae26-0df9-419e-a016-7bc9f61ed2aa",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": -13348.652777777777,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "进制",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "fd900d7a-7642-4d1f-814a-aeb4b4339d6a",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -13615.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "十进制",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "337ee58d-2e6b-4508-a019-81bf420fdb46",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -13375.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "八进制",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "873eaafc-4acf-4cf8-b863-614bfe6e1d4d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -13455.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "首位必须是0，其他位必须是0～7的八进制序列",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "32d85c5d-cce6-473a-ba49-43e9e4ea0962",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -13295.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果后面位数的字面值大于7，则破坏了八进制数据表示规则，前面的0会被忽略，当作十进制数据处理",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "2393339c-868c-4e7e-94b9-9c2cb492609a",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -13055.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "十六进制",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d2d31c14-f6cb-46f4-b102-9a5713f06025",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -13135.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "前两位必须是0x，其他位必须是十六进制序列（0～9，a～f或者A～F）",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "95c5d333-28ef-43af-abbe-e08dcfc5ebac",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -12975.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果超过了十六进制序列，则会抛出异常",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "dd922d77-c6d8-4188-9bd4-6ed8634da4e9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": -12127.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "类型转换规则",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4fc649db-5627-4489-8ddc-5fc64cf768e1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -12735.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Boolean",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4701166c-9b61-43f5-aa04-ad9397a8c733",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -12815.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "true -> 1",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "5e3e1530-0ae5-45d4-9878-36e4ad46f104",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -12655.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "false -> 0",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "50ee914f-b100-458b-942a-5e269c3a2301",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -12495.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Null",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "94d44ab8-0977-47d0-931c-120e09d8b606",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -12495.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "null -> 0",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "2a470e7a-0785-4df8-b23b-5532336ff59f",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -12335.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Undefined",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "de49f7cb-2120-414b-9c5b-78a7b6805746",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -12335.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "undefined -> 0",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "91bac2cf-4805-499c-a28b-7c7eaacbfb61",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -11855.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "String",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b4d88d68-bd79-450f-9085-f1922156adc0",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -12175.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果字符串中只包含数字，则会转换成十进制数；如果前面有0，会直接省略掉",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "ffa5f315-bb0e-42f3-ae77-47522fc917fb",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -12015.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果字符串中包含的是有效的浮点数，则同样按照十进制转换",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "410316c8-5a85-4e3c-9bcb-3c5c2263aeba",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -11855.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果字符串中包含有效的十六进制格式，则会按照十进制转换",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "34860db1-281b-4784-b6dd-f7ba0518358b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -11695.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果是空字符串或连续多个空格，则转换为0",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "39f0d180-85b7-426b-8041-10f710b656cb",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -11535.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果字符串中包含了除上述格式以外的字符串，则会直接转换为NaN",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "c41b3294-43b5-457b-9909-f05189c87330",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -11215.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Object",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "380287d5-b1cf-4d0e-97e5-aebb9748f592",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -11375.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Object类型在转换为Number类型时，会优先调用valueOf()函数，然后通过valueOf()函数的返回值按照上述规则进行转换。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "30b3e444-7a7d-4642-a234-bb868311b058",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -11215.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果转换的结果是NaN，则调用toString()函数，通过toString()函数的返回值重新按照上述规则进行转换；",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "197d7f0a-2188-4040-b8f0-03e1dcac7600",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -11055.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果有确定的Number类型返回值，则结束，否则返回“NaN”。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "fe4e8df6-66ab-4769-bad5-3f6c5d0ff0d7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": -9535.986111111111,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "类型转换方法",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "5c0a351b-43b9-4073-90b7-6c384258bc29",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -10895.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Number()",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b3a8bfa9-44bc-41ca-822b-6462362b238f",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -9927.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "parseInt(string, radix)",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "64112c96-578d-4be0-8f1a-49d8b6ffb5c4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -10575.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "使用",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b24c4b94-e410-4f0d-abaa-6da965ac25ac",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3575.0,
      "y": -10735.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "用于解析一个字符串，并返回指定的基数对应的整数值",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "5f17c6f4-6ca3-42f8-bcb6-1498966a051c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3995.0,
      "y": -10735.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "​",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "9d1f3683-fdf6-45ef-9a33-45f09b2a9611",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3575.0,
      "y": -10575.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "radix表示的是进制转换的基数，数据范围是2～36，默认为10",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e7d852de-99b9-4059-bc93-713194ce1502",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3575.0,
      "y": -10415.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果该字符串无法转换成Number类会返回“NaN”。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "da74c5c5-89a7-45a3-b619-9c756328c64c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -9279.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "特殊场景处理",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "902d961b-cc0c-4038-8129-ce4ab09125fc",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3575.0,
      "y": -10175.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "非字符串类型转换为字符串类型",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "94086ff5-e1f7-4f48-98bc-263b14e81f9a",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3995.0,
      "y": -10175.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果遇到传入的参数是非字符串类型的情况，则需要将其优先转换成字符串类型，即使传入的是整型数据。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "1ba6cd98-7c1e-477b-ba1b-bc8e863325b6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4415.0,
      "y": -10255.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "parseInt('0x12', 16); // 18",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "c8c9dbf1-55f1-4c05-8308-dcc415668af7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4835.0,
      "y": -10255.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "直接将字符串\"0x12\"转换为十六进制数，得到的结果为1×16+2=18；",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "be47d8d5-dbb3-4a6d-a3dd-d17f9452b3fe",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4415.0,
      "y": -10095.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "parseInt(0x12, 16); // 24",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "c947db0d-c6a6-432e-84f0-a1c911a9b993",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4835.0,
      "y": -10095.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "由于传入的是十六进制数，所以会先转换成十进制数18，然后转换成字符串\"18\"，再将字符串\"18\"转换成十六进制数，得到的结果为1×16+8=24。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "06e418ee-d7da-4d26-bf2e-41b222ecb8f6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3575.0,
      "y": -9775.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "数据截取的前置匹配原则",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "659fafc7-a4b8-40f2-9bb9-644ab7e60619",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3995.0,
      "y": -9775.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "parseInt()函数在做转换时，对于传入的字符串会采用前置匹配的原则",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "cb667d55-e263-43cf-8831-22eda21ff683",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4415.0,
      "y": -9775.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "即从字符串的第一个字符开始匹配，如果处于基数指定的范围，则保留并继续往后匹配满足条件的字符，直到某个字符不满足基数指定的数据范围，则从该字符开始，舍弃后面的全部字符。在获取到满足条件的字符后，将这些字符转换为整数。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e02b7056-476d-40b6-9534-39c2fce43e2a",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4835.0,
      "y": -9935.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "parseInt(\"fg123\", 16);  // 15",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4680cdb6-f627-480e-afc3-0c764ad89c20",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 5255.0,
      "y": -9935.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "对于字符串'fg123'，首先从第一个字符开始，'f'是满足十六进制的数据，因为十六进制数据范围是0～9，a～f(A～F)，所以保留'f'；然后是第二个字符'g'，它不满足十六进制数据范围，因此从第二个字符至最后一个字符全部舍弃，最终字符串只保留字符'f'；然后将字符'f'转换成十六进制的数据，为15，因此最后返回的结果为“15”。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "1a807784-fec0-4514-a320-ae001f97a029",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4835.0,
      "y": -9775.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "parseInt('0x12',16);   // 18 = 16 + 2\nparseInt('0x12',10);   // 0",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "1d732fb0-5deb-4efb-913f-37ed84436f84",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 5255.0,
      "y": -9775.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果遇到的字符串是以\"0x\"开头的，那么在按照十六进制处理时，会计算后面满足条件的字符串；如果按照十进制处理，则会直接返回“0”。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e9d1d79e-3fd4-4dfb-855b-e313d81b685e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4835.0,
      "y": -9615.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "parseInt(15 * 3, 10);   // 45，先运算完成得到45，再进行parseInt(45, 10)的运算\nparseInt('15 * 3', 10); // 15，直接当作字符串处理，并不会进行乘法运算",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "250450bf-7188-47ee-b6af-7d1aca65ad6b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 5255.0,
      "y": -9615.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果传入的字符串中涉及算术运算，则不执行，算术符号会被当作字符处理；如果传入的参数是算术运算表达式，则会先运算完成得到结果，再参与parseInt()函数的计算。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "9e2813eb-2e51-4a35-ae14-a9b8734ecb25",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3575.0,
      "y": -9215.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "对包含字符e的不同数据的处理差异",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "ce18329d-5467-4e9f-9baa-e297eeb0529b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3995.0,
      "y": -9375.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "当传入的参数本身就是Number类型时",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "c4a4edad-7b4d-4927-b03a-f2cc2853b0ef",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4415.0,
      "y": -9375.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "会将e按照科学计数法计算后转换成字符串，然后按照对应的基数转换得到最终的结果。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "ccce2c46-6ab5-46a1-88f7-e00cf314e382",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4835.0,
      "y": -9455.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "parseInt(6e3, 10);     // 6000",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d207d4d0-8334-4f23-80c0-04fd15173025",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 5255.0,
      "y": -9455.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "首先会执行6e3=6000，然后转换为字符串\"6000\"，实际执行的语句是parseInt('6000', 10)，表示的是将字符串\"6000\"转换为十进制的整数，得到的结果为6000。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "f8cee7e8-c2a7-40b7-a03f-3cdf4fdd7089",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4835.0,
      "y": -9295.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "parseInt(6e3, 16); // 24576",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "1bb64591-38b4-4ae3-9690-4c94751bbcb8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 5255.0,
      "y": -9295.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "首先会执行6e3=6000，然后转换为字符串\"6000\"，实际执行的语句是parseInt('6000', 16)，表示的是将字符串\"6000\"转换为十六进制的数，得到的结果是6×163 = 24576",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "88a880ea-034e-456d-912a-15e33066d809",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3995.0,
      "y": -9055.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果传入的字符串中直接包含e",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "ae7e734d-a65c-4c7f-86ca-8a552fc3a2fa",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4415.0,
      "y": -9055.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "那么并不会按照科学计数法处理，而是会判断字符e是否处在可处理的进制范围内，如果不在则直接忽略，如果在则转换成对应的进制数。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "6ce5180c-835c-4df4-8146-4bc4797dea4a",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4835.0,
      "y": -9135.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "parseInt('6e3', 10);    // 6",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "fd59ea0c-ec6a-4dc5-bac6-5d24d8d45877",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 5255.0,
      "y": -9135.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "表示的是将字符串'6e3'转换为十进制的整数，因为字符'e'不在十进制所能表达的范围内，所以会直接省略，实际处理的字符串只有\"6\"，得到的结果为6。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "636f1601-6a56-458d-bcd3-5dbe1c5a760f",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4835.0,
      "y": -8975.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "parseInt('6e3', 16); // 1763",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e2b3e9c4-cdeb-4500-b813-373086db0a88",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 5255.0,
      "y": -8975.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "表示的是将字符串'6e3'转换为十六进制的整数，因为字符'e'在十六进制所能表达的范围内，所以会转换为14进行计算，最后得到的结果为6×162 +14×16 + 3 = 1763。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e7d36c7a-cc3d-4732-9767-bc4ddb6a0724",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3575.0,
      "y": -8815.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "对浮点型数的处理",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "7097c849-1de0-456d-b66b-5750b2f0ca90",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3995.0,
      "y": -8815.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果传入的值是浮点型数，则会忽略小数点及后面的数，直接取整。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "699c72be-8ff8-403b-a261-fca8d88c7325",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3575.0,
      "y": -8415.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "map()函数与parseInt()函数的隐形坑",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4c4b8c32-8040-4217-9264-d61c3df4f551",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3995.0,
      "y": -8415.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "var arr = ['1', '2', '3', '4'];\nvar result = arr.map(parseInt);\n\nconsole.log(result);\n\n但是在运行后，得到的结果是[1, NaN, NaN, NaN]，与我们期望的结果[1, 2, 3, 4]差别很大，这是为什么呢？",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "22f10745-57d1-4d0c-9ae1-e4866a73e525",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4415.0,
      "y": -8415.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "arr.map(parseInt);\n\n与下面代码等效\n\narr.map(function (val, index) {\n\n    return parseInt(val, index);\n\n});",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "0873f3c4-49e6-4034-bc7e-3401fae5ede1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4835.0,
      "y": -8415.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "parseInt()函数接收的第二个参数实际为数组的索引值，所以实际处理的过程如下所示。\n\nparseInt('1', 0);  // 1\n\nparseInt('2', 1);  // NaN\n\nparseInt('3', 2);  // NaN\n\nparseInt('4', 3);  // NaN",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "27bd0f2f-245b-44e5-92fd-d1d3df38577c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 5255.0,
      "y": -8655.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "任何整数以0为基数取整时，都会返回本身，所以第一行代码会返回“1”。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "14dca723-8896-41f8-8c4d-d43ae05c6fc6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 5255.0,
      "y": -8495.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "第二行代码parseInt('2', 1)，因为parseInt()函数对应的基数只能为2～36，不满足基数的整数在处理后会返回“NaN”；",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d85102c1-a7f3-4c96-b99c-ab991dc08e60",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 5255.0,
      "y": -8335.319444444445,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "第三行代码parseInt('3', 2)，表示的是将3处理为二进制表示，实际上二进制时只有0和1，3超出了二进制的表示范围，无法转换，返回“NaN”；",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "46533952-7eb5-490e-ad41-365328c8695a",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 5255.0,
      "y": -8175.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "第四行代码parseInt('4', 3)，与第三行类似，4无法用三进制的数据表示，返回“NaN”。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "862f13b6-b661-4b29-a526-6064c4a5417b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -7785.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "parseFloat()",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "dfe9837d-f323-4652-a6b1-b52df8312d16",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -8015.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "用于解析一个字符串，返回对应的浮点数。如果给定值不能转换为数值，则会返回“NaN”。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "344f3e06-49d2-478c-93e5-e5635064fc06",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -7555.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "与parseInt()函数相比，parseFloat()函数没有进制的概念，所以在转换时会相对简单些，但是仍有以下一些需要注意的地方。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "62b4bd60-0833-44f8-85eb-5f79288ab95f",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3575.0,
      "y": -7855.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果在解析过程中遇到了正负号（+ / -）、数字0～9、小数点或者科学计数法（e /E）以外的字符，则会忽略从该字符开始至结束的所有字符，然后返回当前已经解析的字符的浮点数形式。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "634e92c4-e094-46e2-b015-2e9834b6e1e2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3995.0,
      "y": -7855.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "正负号必须出现在字符的第一位，而且不能连续出现。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "19fdf463-32a2-45bd-95ca-70840af0af34",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4415.0,
      "y": -7855.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "parseFloat('+1.2');   // 1.2\nparseFloat('-1.2');   // -1.2\n\nparseFloat('++1.2');  // NaN，符号不能连续出现\n\nparseFloat('--1.2');  // NaN，符号不能连续出现\n\nparseFloat('1+1.2');  // 1，'+'出现在第二位，不会当作符号位处理",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "6c2ea023-e8ce-4916-8581-7f9a49786d41",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3575.0,
      "y": -7695.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "字符串前面的空白符会直接忽略，如果第一个字符就无法解析，则会直接返回“NaN”。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b0b1b8aa-1ec1-43e4-a475-b123ceb0713b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3995.0,
      "y": -7695.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "parseFloat('  1.2'); // 1.2\nparseFloat('f1.2');  // NaN",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "77dfedb0-c3d7-46fb-aa1e-f4dd6bdfcf14",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3575.0,
      "y": -7455.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "对于字符串中出现的合法科学运算符e，进行运算处理后会转换成浮点型数，这点与parseInt()函数的处理有很大的不同。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "0469a23c-63bb-4685-8062-9ca270863f45",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3995.0,
      "y": -7535.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "parseFloat('4e3');   // 4000",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "1e9b9739-58b0-4001-8e28-0078579e6f61",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4415.0,
      "y": -7535.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "parseFloat()函数在处理'4e3'时，会先进行科学计数法的运算，即4e3 = 4×1000 =4000，然后转换成浮点型数，返回“4000”；",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "51d18571-bbdb-4a88-aa62-7d5da255eea9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3995.0,
      "y": -7375.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "parseInt('4e3', 10); // 4",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "7fc28c24-5c3e-4c09-aba0-29fb547bca1d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 4415.0,
      "y": -7375.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "parseInt()函数在以十进制处理'4e3'时，不会进行科学计数法的运算，而是直接从第一个字符开始匹配，最终匹配成功的字符为'4'，转换成整型后，返回整数“4”。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "87bc5c35-8087-45f5-924a-4761d7d7db93",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3575.0,
      "y": -7215.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "对于小数点，只能正确匹配第一个，第二个小数点是无效的，它后面的字符也都将被忽略。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4c1de47c-1d34-4d5e-8025-5fa35cb70d85",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3995.0,
      "y": -7215.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "parseFloat('11.20');  // 11.2\nparseFloat('11.2.1'); // 11.2",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "598fbb3d-a413-4cfa-95b7-6228ff36a41b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": -6559.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "isNaN()函数与Number.isNaN()函数对比",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "83665448-6a65-4f1f-8103-bffd5a007e15",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -7055.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "什么是NaN",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "fea92279-ed6a-43ce-bcac-13b91e2e5639",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -7055.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Number类型数据中存在一个比较特殊的数值NaN（Not a Number），它表示应该返回数值却并未返回数值的情况。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "848527d6-6086-4bd3-a019-2c236e362985",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -6815.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "NaN特点",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a90f45bc-06bd-4acc-9166-8cd062d62a15",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -6895.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "任何涉及NaN的操作都会返回“NaN”",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "48ab2bd0-2e21-4ee0-8e78-f09cddd29efa",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -6735.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "NaN与任何值都不相等，即使是与NaN本身相比",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e55178a4-0cec-499d-89ee-217c280c8f5b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3575.0,
      "y": -6735.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "NaN == NaN;  // false",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "6058efc7-6e83-4948-9161-cb4180b9d638",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -6575.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "isNaN函数",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "203896d8-8c3e-4695-a828-edd878d9cf42",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -6575.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "isNaN()函数会进行数据的类型转换，它在处理的时候会去判断传入的变量值能否转换为数字，如果能转换成数字则会返回“false”，如果无法转换则会返回“true”。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "1fca56d6-ac36-4cda-b360-c866e0968856",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -6335.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Number.isNaN()函数",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "6dd2c705-abc8-4bf2-a72c-7d33484549ac",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -6415.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "isNaN()函数本身存在误导性，而ES6中的Number.isNaN()函数会在真正意义上去判断变量是否为NaN，不会做数据类型转换。只有在传入的值为NaN时，才会返回“true”，传入其他任何类型的值时会返回“false”。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a050bc6b-ad35-4751-a845-7517731d5b57",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -6255.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果在非ES6环境中想用ES6中的isNaN()函数，该怎么办呢？我们有以下兼容性处理方案。\n\n// 兼容性处理\n\nif(!Number.isNaN) {\n\n    Number.isNaN = function (n) {\n\n       return n !== n;\n\n    }\n\n}",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "c050062c-b93d-4ba6-8bf0-aca3ac8dc817",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -6015.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "总结",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "47ad86f9-8363-4916-86c2-7671a71606b8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -6095.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "isNaN()函数在判断是否为NaN时，需要先进行数据类型转换，只有在无法转换为数字时才会返回“true”；",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d9aab2df-d224-403b-998c-958ed4d035c4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -5935.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Number.isNaN()函数在判断是否为NaN时，只需要判断传入的值是否为NaN，并不会进行数据类型转换。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "cee5706e-d2be-4b66-9f7d-14105282f6c3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": -5255.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "浮点型运算",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "1e87e096-14a9-41b5-9b5c-0277cfa4b282",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -5775.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "问题",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "7c4adc37-de86-4bb8-83ec-1f74c85d42a9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -5775.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "// 加法\n0.1 + 0.2 = 0.30000000000000004\n\n0.7 + 0.1 = 0.7999999999999999\n\n// 减法\n\n1.5 - 1.2 = 0.30000000000000004\n\n0.3 - 0.2 = 0.09999999999999998\n\n// 乘法\n\n0.7 * 180 = 125.99999999999999\n\n9.7 * 100 = 969.9999999999999\n\n// 除法\n\n0.3 / 0.1 = 2.9999999999999996\n\n0.69 / 10 = 0.06899999999999999",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "17b3ec85-1d66-4a64-aa01-730164587a93",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -5175.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "问题原因",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "bf071a8f-4e37-4345-baf3-60c8c0c3f66f",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -5375.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "一个浮点型数在计算机中的表示，它总共长度是64位，其中最高位为符号位，接下来的11位为指数位，最后的52位为小数位，即有效数字的部分。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "648e5505-68dc-45f1-b8b2-e08ad0f0093a",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3575.0,
      "y": -5615.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "第0位：符号位sign表示数的正负，0表示正数，1表示负数。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "8e4523ec-5d07-4293-80de-c5f9478ce20f",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3575.0,
      "y": -5455.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "第1位到第11位：存储指数部分，用e表示。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "acd7e98e-17a1-47f8-8350-dd87d3f3b84e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3575.0,
      "y": -5295.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "第12位到第63位：存储小数部分（即有效数字），用f表示",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "3493269e-a867-429c-8344-b4515dac1fa7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3575.0,
      "y": -5135.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "3493269e-a867-429c-8344-b4515dac1fa7",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "88d64a14-0557-407f-a592-eb1b2c88fcf6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -4975.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "因为浮点型数使用64位存储时，最多只能存储52位的小数位，对于一些存在无限循环的小数位浮点数，会截取前52位，从而丢失精度，所以会出现上面实例中的结果。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d9ff0b11-467d-47a6-b9ed-c047a0d27f26",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -4815.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "解决方案",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "23b15bb8-16ae-465f-815e-0c5cbfef4718",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -4815.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "将浮点数先乘以一定的数值转换为整数，通过整数进行运算，然后将结果除以相同的数值转换成浮点数后返回。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "873bc2fa-f475-4af9-98ce-be2f79e1e1e1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1895.0,
      "y": -3193.9861111111113,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "String",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e49665eb-a006-4eda-9812-e9314d1ac99b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": -4495.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "定义方式",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a6c87fc1-90e4-43f7-9a9d-550eb9774d00",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -4655.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "字符串字面量",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "db1ae9a7-4174-4289-88dc-723a8032f9d6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -4655.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "直接通过单引号或者双引号定义字符串的方式",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a2ede761-2db5-4d80-bd0d-1520a1feff40",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3575.0,
      "y": -4655.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "返回基本字符串",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "29e130d5-ddc9-479e-96f5-f550c14c42a9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -4495.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "调用String()",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "9e2a51ec-b0d3-4fbe-a9d5-3ccc3162da01",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -4495.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "返回基本字符串",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "7a84fe0b-e5de-4eb7-be22-41fa94a88276",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -4335.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "new String()",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "70dfb405-9914-4754-9330-a1a053c82c70",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -4335.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "返回值是一个String类型对象的实例",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "04981ac7-40d4-44b9-b994-d951fe187dfc",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": -3748.652777777778,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "转换规则",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "80f687d0-b891-4d4d-9da6-5ce2f7ae0992",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -4175.319444444444,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "1.Number转换成对应的字符串",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "27633762-aae6-43db-b6cf-a29412f10948",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -4015.3194444444443,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "2.Boolean转换成'true'或者'false'",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "0f340037-cfaa-4baa-aa36-1612a901c225",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -3855.3194444444443,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "3.null返回字符串'null'",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "237216a7-7cab-4101-a718-846c5c7248d1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -3695.3194444444443,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "4.undefined返回字符串'undefined'",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "69b835a8-ce4d-4b9e-8481-34845cfeb6c7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -3535.3194444444443,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "5.字符串返回字符串本身",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "c1d268ae-0a7c-43f8-b379-1b4100ecbb7c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -3215.3194444444443,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "引用类型",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "91662174-b0e4-4596-a0ae-b7d0f10e2225",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -3375.3194444444443,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "先调用toString()函数获取返回值，将返回值按照上述步骤①～⑤判断能否转换字符串类型",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "47bf9be7-4d8a-4ea0-af1b-58b0f453ee80",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -3215.3194444444443,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果都不满足，则会调用对象的valueOf()函数获取返回值，并将返回值重新按照步骤①～⑤判断能否转换成字符串类型",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "f4b30de4-7acf-4487-8e7a-25dd7e6bd657",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -3055.3194444444443,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果也不满足，则会抛出类型转换的异常。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "fa54021a-db4a-4599-8041-63484db36745",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": -2895.3194444444443,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "三种定义方式的区别",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "89b4006e-2d6f-4ca3-b112-421ccec8b1cc",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -2895.3194444444443,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "使用第一种字符串字面量方式和第二种直接调用String()函数的方式得到的字符串都是基本字符串，而通过第三种方式，new运算符生成的字符串是字符串对象。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "caff3ce7-ccb0-4e7b-a686-25c912a83a87",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": -2575.3194444444443,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "函数的调用",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "09db5228-ed63-406d-aff2-9c3146871b53",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -2735.3194444444443,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "字面量方式定义的字符串可以调用原型链上的函数",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e76c9ca1-c31c-4c54-a0a1-0a3e4e919db4",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -2575.3194444444443,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "基本字符串本身是没有字符串对象的函数，而在基本字符串调用字符串对象才有的函数时，JavaScript会自动将基本字符串转换为字符串对象，形成一种包装类型，这样基本字符串就可以正常调用字符串对象的方法了",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "13484fbe-ee0f-4590-962c-3b9b1e351985",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -2415.3194444444443,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "基本字符串和字符串对象在经过eval()函数处理时，会产生不同的结果",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "5ca93a50-4b1a-4e2d-abc0-a7e72d5191a8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -2415.3194444444443,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "eval()函数会将基本字符串作为源代码处理，如果涉及表达式会直接进行运算，返回运算后的结果；而字符串对象则会被看作对象处理，返回对象本身。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "ba88296e-5dc2-444c-a6c0-1a2f07b1d0c3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3575.0,
      "y": -2415.3194444444443,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "var s1 = '2 + 2';               // 创建一个字符串字面量\nvar s2 = new String('2 + 2');   // 创建一个对象字符串\n\nconsole.log(eval(s1));          // 4\n\nconsole.log(eval(s2));          // String {\"2 + 2\"}",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "7157b7da-c269-4cf6-ac10-4044ea10e86a",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": -2255.3194444444443,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "String类型常见算法",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "943797c8-c188-4c59-a99f-3ba71817ae53",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1895.0,
      "y": -2095.3194444444443,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Symbol",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b28a8ea2-2278-4371-b2b4-417e8ac407df",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1475.0,
      "y": -1295.3194444444443,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Undefined和Null两种类型的异同",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a573a091-d2e6-4319-b1e6-86ec81abc245",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1895.0,
      "y": -1695.3194444444443,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "相同点",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "58f95473-0f52-4a3d-b983-a2e812b45d57",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": -1935.3194444444443,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Undefined和Null两种数据类型都只有一个字面值，分别是undefined和null。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "f4613e47-cce5-46b4-93b2-64426f0559ac",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": -1775.3194444444443,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Undefined类型和Null类型在转换为Boolean类型的值时，都会转换为false",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "f3245491-4395-4cec-be65-d5eac214415b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": -1615.3194444444443,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在需要将两者转换成对象时，都会抛出一个TypeError的异常，也就是平时最常见的引用异常",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "92f38bb9-1913-4743-9395-5123e1289eda",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": -1455.3194444444443,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Undefined类型派生自Null类型，所以在非严格相等的情况下，两者是相等的",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "23496f10-3a2c-4784-b004-c66ad89696f6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1895.0,
      "y": -895.3194444444443,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "不同点",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "0c31cc17-2b9f-40ff-8425-4b66bad7d3b9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": -1295.3194444444443,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "null是JavaScript中的关键字，而undefined是JavaScript中的一个全局变量，即挂载在window对象上的一个变量，并不是关键字",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "5e80faca-54ce-46f6-bde6-97efb9b8560b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": -1135.3194444444443,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在使用typeof运算符检测时，Undefined类型的值会返回“undefined”，而Null类型的值会返回“object”",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d7c0c82c-60f2-48ae-b019-4533dbf39d55",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": -975.3194444444443,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在通过call调用toString()函数时，Undefined类型的值会返回“[objectUndefined]”，而Null类型的值会返回“[object Null]”",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "59d67468-f0aa-46ff-a06d-7252855c98db",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": -815.3194444444443,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在需要进行字符串类型的转换时，null会转换为字符串\"null\"，而undefined会转换为字符串\"undefined\"",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "2dcc2c09-aca6-4935-ae18-ce20d3da894c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": -655.3194444444443,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在需要进行数值类型的转换时，undefined会转换为NaN，无法参与计算；null会转换为0，可以参与计算",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "1827b525-3b2e-4028-bf82-a0fcccab75dd",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": -495.31944444444434,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "无论在什么情况下都没有必要将一个变量显式设置为undefined。如果需要定义某个变量来保存将来要使用的对象，应该将其初始化为null。这样不仅能将null作为空对象指针的惯例，还有助于区分null和undefined",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "8cd7a86e-3a16-4e94-b6c9-013894641a5b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1475.0,
      "y": 1530.0972222222226,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "运算符",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "1c640b54-89a4-4d5a-8ea3-a5e4daf48232",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1895.0,
      "y": 89.68055555555566,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "== / ===",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "ac317284-da0d-449d-a1ea-ba5a76a485c7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": -215.31944444444434,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "三等运算符",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "686ca8d8-fb8c-4c90-8904-2c2f360e2df7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -335.31944444444434,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "优先比较数据类型，数据类型相同才去判断值的大小，如果类型不同则直接返回“false”",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e66a88be-ae0a-4abd-99bd-192845558b1e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": -95.31944444444434,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "注意",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "c7307738-76c6-4c92-83f7-eb5f6a3eff24",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -175.31944444444434,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在未使用new操作符时，简单类型的比较实际为值的比较，而使用了new操作符后，实际得到的是引用类型的值，在判断时会因为类型不同而直接返回“false”",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "1b7ce26c-2d2f-4381-98eb-35eac407b224",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": -15.319444444444343,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "参与比较的值中有任何一方为NaN，返回“false”",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b9d62b54-353c-4afa-82c5-4268047fd6ef",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": 394.68055555555566,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "双等运算符",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "44a64f87-5562-48c0-9648-311d7e1742b9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": 144.68055555555566,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "将两端的变量进行隐式类型转换，然后比较值的大小",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "3847356e-1978-4d21-bc07-48a08b3af91e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": 644.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "类型转换规则",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "15ed852f-7284-4c3f-bb33-6e2f6643a3b2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": 304.68055555555566,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果比较的一方是null或者undefined，只有在另一方是null或者undefined的情况下才返回“true”，否则返回“false”",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "ade572e4-931f-47b9-be6b-7cc291f8f5a5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": 544.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果比较的是字符串和数值类型数据，则会将字符串转换为数值后再进行比较，如果转换后的数值相等则返回“true”，否则返回“false”",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "8dc9033d-5c8b-42fe-9cd9-04ca75bab565",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3575.0,
      "y": 464.68055555555566,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "字符串是十六进制的数据，会转换为十进制后再进行比较",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "fb1b7c4f-1b0e-4e9d-9771-cab3adba7463",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3575.0,
      "y": 624.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "字符串并不支持八进制的数据，如果字符串以0开头，则0会直接省略，后面的值当作十进制返回",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "41b560cf-1a69-4ded-a9b5-664dd287c4ac",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": 784.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果任一类型是boolean值，则会将boolean类型的值进行转换，true转换为1，false转换为0，然后进行比较",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "9c551a45-3270-4130-8489-f6797e9a5fc5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": 944.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果其中一个值是对象类型，另一个值是基本数据类型或者对象类型，则会调用对象的valueOf()函数或者toString()函数，将其转换成基本数据类型后再作比较",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e37250e2-926f-4f63-9e3c-aca2f127d996",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1895.0,
      "y": 1291.3472222222226,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "typeof",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "71b7f227-33cb-4de5-b0ed-c240c6664613",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": 1104.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "用于返回操作数的数据类型",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "8ebdca76-9be5-4af2-aa36-661536687d15",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": 1264.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "规则",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4d3aed84-988e-47c6-8418-a7ca41e6d43e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": 1264.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "4d3aed84-988e-47c6-8418-a7ca41e6d43e",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "df635eaa-f705-48e0-9afd-b533e79cc580",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": 1504.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "疑问",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "fd5ee0c2-997a-443e-ac6f-975ce170f32d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": 1424.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "typeof运算符区分对待Object类型和Function类型",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "39a78362-1eb6-45c7-b427-6acb0465a213",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": 1424.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "从技术角度讲，函数在ECMAScript中是对象，不是一种数据类型。然而，函数也确实有一些特殊的属性，因此通过typeof运算符来区分函数和其他对象是有必要的",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d9911b24-c493-46b6-8f5a-cfcec894ac2b",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": 1584.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "typeof运算符对null的处理",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "5e554d46-22b1-4f3f-b4bc-ac6769ad2656",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": 1584.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在JavaScript中，每种数据类型都会使用3bit表示。\n· 000表示Object类型的数据\n\n· 001表示Int类型的数据\n\n· 010表示Double类型的数据。\n\n· 100表示String类型的数据。\n\n· 110表示Boolean类型的数据。\n\n由于null代表的是空指针，大多数平台中值为0x00，因此null的类型标签就成了0，所以使用typeof运算符时会判断为object类型，返回“object”。虽然在后面的提案中有提出修复方案，但是因为影响面太大，所以并没有被采纳，从而导致这个问题一直存在。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "2d3debf7-7092-45a8-bcd1-cae957343df2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1895.0,
      "y": 1954.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": ",",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "6915e45a-d568-4425-adfe-cc98ae37b01c",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": 1744.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "将多个表达式连接起来，从左至右依次执行",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d6cf298a-f1ca-4e44-95c4-e4edb8f229ae",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": 2164.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "使用场景",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "0c5405f0-2045-47f6-92d2-b30a02502bb7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": 1904.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "在for循环中批量执行表达式",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "187c3e21-3347-48f2-a8d6-416a7a62f6bd",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": 1904.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "for (var i = 0, j = 10; i < 10, j < 20; i++, j++) {\n   console.log(i, j); \n\n}",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "9ae7f881-5592-4ec2-b849-60394b15d540",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": 2064.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "交换变量，无须额外变量",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a2e78556-fab7-4539-afb9-b24fd8efc886",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": 2064.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "var a = 'a';\nvar b = 'b';\n\n// 方案1\n\na = [b, b = a][0];\n\n// 方案2\n\na = [b][b = a, 0];",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b68e22e3-9133-446e-b2b4-10a12b303bf5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": 2224.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "简化代码",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "7606f9fd-7926-4e10-882c-4cd62b35d0dc",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": 2224.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "if (x) {\n   foo();\n\n   return bar();\n\n} else {\n\n   return 1;\n\n}\n\n// 使用逗号运算符简写后\n\nx ? (foo(), bar()) : 1;",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "94067565-4183-4bbb-bcf5-8ac7514da4f3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": 2464.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "用小括号保证逗号运算符的优先级",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "fcd1f769-4ac3-4954-bc0a-0337daa194e0",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": 2384.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "var a = 20;\nvar b = ++a, 10;\n\nconsole.log(b);  // Uncaught SyntaxError: Unexpected number",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d21d2e14-ff7b-440b-af4c-ba77e8f62ca6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": 2544.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "var a = 20;\nvar b = (++a, 10);\n\nconsole.log(b);  // 10",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "6c154718-5c80-40de-93ce-4e99ecb0f1ca",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1895.0,
      "y": 2784.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "优先级",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "21aacfd3-c225-4c68-82df-3fb411c0b8ca",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": 2704.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "21aacfd3-c225-4c68-82df-3fb411c0b8ca",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "92e15e91-dc45-49d9-9c78-384075798bf5",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": 2864.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "92e15e91-dc45-49d9-9c78-384075798bf5",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b5ac99e6-d722-4adf-a219-62f7986e5cef",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1475.0,
      "y": 4424.680555555556,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "toString() 和 valueOf()",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4efee453-f682-4bed-9658-67985ce327ab",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1895.0,
      "y": 3264.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "toString()",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "8e0ff8ca-14e4-4a2f-ab86-6a1386e22587",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": 3264.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "作用",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "537fe90b-79b3-4118-b218-479405a36af0",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": 3264.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "把一个逻辑值转换为字符串，并返回结果",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "f0c37208-92f8-46f8-89dd-d21a7bdb57b3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": 3024.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Object",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "be247945-5655-4558-9800-bffb16095085",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3575.0,
      "y": 3024.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "\"[object Object]\"",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d002d0c5-1ebb-40b7-a10d-58e3b2d08295",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": 3184.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Array",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "247d367e-a3eb-4c20-bc7f-89c0542ade04",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3575.0,
      "y": 3184.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "以逗号分隔构成的数组成员字符串，例如[1, 2,3].toString()结果为字符串'1,2,3'。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "793ea589-2b6d-4408-b451-50cb199588e2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": 3344.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Function",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "6364aff3-6759-4440-a806-d004cfcfbed1",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3575.0,
      "y": 3344.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "函数的文本定义，例如(function(x){return x *2;}).toString()的结果为字符串\"function(x){return x * 2;}\"。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "0e54f7e4-432e-4ab2-a9a0-e564de36a831",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": 3504.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Date",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "a874be16-181f-450b-96c6-fcde5bfd87fb",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3575.0,
      "y": 3504.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "具有可读性的时间字符串，例如，new Date().toString()的结果为字符串\"Sun Nov 25 201815:00:16 GMT+0800 (中国标准时间)\"",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "44fb1f22-c6ef-443d-abfd-c3e22790b40f",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1895.0,
      "y": 3904.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "valueOf()",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "29aed544-329a-4efc-90ff-c9b794518dbc",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": 3904.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "作用",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "93e3aea6-3124-4d44-913f-1f2b6d0cd7f3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": 3904.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "返回最适合引用类型的原始值，如果没有原始值，则会返回引用类型自身",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e674b9c2-dda0-48c9-b6ca-2e39f360cd29",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": 3664.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Object",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "acc7e8a1-350c-4935-b7d8-dba711b76fa9",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3575.0,
      "y": 3664.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "\"{}\"，即一个空的对象字面量",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b155c3d9-58fe-4621-b2f0-9da14959ff58",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": 3824.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Array",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "8734a0cf-6f34-4900-9df9-07e7c70e898a",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3575.0,
      "y": 3824.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "返回的是数组本身，例如[1, 2, 3].valueOf()返回的结果为“[1,2,3]”",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "52cdb70b-0544-460a-8120-df2112852043",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": 3984.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Function",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "85130869-ad4c-46e0-a622-50b43225d8f7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3575.0,
      "y": 3984.6805555555557,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "返回的是函数本身，例如(function(x){return x * 2;}).valueOf()返回的结果为函数本身“function(x){return x * 2;}”",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "f6df99b5-d811-4331-a1d2-65b5b3284d1d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3155.0,
      "y": 4144.680555555556,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Date",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "26be6d12-f86a-459e-b16a-30681c538192",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 3575.0,
      "y": 4144.680555555556,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "返回的是指定日期的时间戳，例如newDate().valueOf()返回的结果为“1543130166771”",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "d9fc35ff-5ecd-4ad7-b0c0-267c0a0e4643",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1895.0,
      "y": 4464.680555555556,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "引用类型转换为String类型",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "db4f99dc-1055-4895-b463-f75587a0bd69",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": 4304.680555555556,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果对象具有toString()函数，则会优先调用toString()函数。如果它返回的是一个原始值，则会直接将这个原始值转换为字符串表",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "424b3647-ffb7-4174-9966-0981b923891d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": 4464.680555555556,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果对象没有toString()函数，或者toString()函数返回的不是一个原始值，则会再去调用valueOf()函数，如果valueOf()函数返回的结果是一个原始值，则会将这个结果转换为字符串表示，并返回该字符串。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b120e59b-fd38-46ef-853c-0f09015a358d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": 4624.680555555556,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果通过toString()函数或者valueOf()函数都无法获得一个原始值，则会直接抛出类型转换异常。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "66c6d292-4d36-4f96-af0b-fa0183f23b5a",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1895.0,
      "y": 4944.680555555556,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "引用类型转换为Number类型",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "bfcd7126-15a4-46d4-afc8-f620a6c8a678",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": 4784.680555555556,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果对象具有valueOf()函数，则会优先调用valueOf()函数，如果valueOf()函数返回一个原始值，则会直接将这个原始值转换为数字表示，并返回该数字。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "26990ba9-722e-4048-b13f-7c32f01276b0",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": 4944.680555555556,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果对象没有valueOf()函数，或者valueOf()函数返回的不是原生数据类型，则会再去调用toString()函数，如果toString()函数返回的结果是一个原始值，则会将这个结果转换为数字表示，并返回该数字。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "833c16d8-d523-4120-b9c9-e17d8e5cd1f6",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": 5104.680555555556,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "如果通过toString()函数或者valueOf()函数都无法获得一个原始值，则会直接抛出类型转换异常。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "97671148-3508-46e4-b188-443e1ed65140",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1895.0,
      "y": 5544.680555555556,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "拓展",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "2f17bd8f-1096-45c3-a41c-3b088d9ebb2e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": 5344.680555555556,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "[] == 0; // true\n[1] == 1; // true\n\n[2] == 2; // true",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "da79ca57-0d35-45e8-b00c-cace16d637a3",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": 5264.680555555556,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "数组继承了Object类型默认的valueOf()函数，这个函数返回的是数组自身，而不是原生数据类型",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "8a91e215-cf39-46a9-81c9-543140b31d29",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": 5424.680555555556,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "所以会继续调用toString()函数。数组调用toString()函数时会返回数组元素以逗号作为分隔符构成的字符串，那么空数组就转换为空字符串，而空字符串与数字0在非严格相等的情况下是相等的，即'' == 0，返回“true”。同样，只包含一个数字的数组[1]，转换后为字符串\"1\"，后判断\"1\" ==1，返回“true”。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "0627dc11-c712-46c5-ba83-27521d5a1003",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": 5744.680555555556,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "var obj = {\n     i: 10,\n\n     toString: function () {\n\n         console.log('toString');\n\n         return this.i;\n\n     },\n\n     valueOf: function () {\n\n         console.log('valueOf');\n\n         return this.i;\n\n     }\n\n};\n\n+obj;  // valueOf\n\n'' + obj;  // valueOf\n\nString(obj);  // toString\n\nNumber(obj);  // valueOf\n\nobj == '10';  // valueOf，true\n\nobj === '10'; // false",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "0409e52f-7720-4b7e-b55c-7b45e4c5b8c8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": 5584.680555555556,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "+obj、'' + obj、Number(obj)、obj == '10'，将对象obj转换为原始值，用于数据运算，优先调用valueOf()函数，获得原始值，结果为数字“10”",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "9251efa6-c569-48e7-87ba-409257e81674",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": 5744.680555555556,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "String(obj)，在String()函数中，用于数据展示，优先调用toString()函数获取对象的字符串表示，结果为字符串\"10\"。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "29652d54-4613-44d8-be99-02cdc4c47aed",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": 5904.680555555556,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "obj === '10'，因为两者数据类型不一致，直接返回“false”，并不会执行toString()函数或者valueOf()函数。",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "53bbee31-953c-4573-add2-14102573dce2",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1475.0,
      "y": 6736.680555555556,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "常用的判空方法",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "efdd86df-820b-4f44-a657-32a1b43f21e7",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1895.0,
      "y": 6064.680555555556,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "判断变量为null或者undefined",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "31602ab9-ef8f-4403-b9b3-cefa5f859975",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": 6064.680555555556,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "if(obj == null) {} // 可以判断null或者undeﬁned\n\nif(obj === undeﬁned) {} // 只能判断undeﬁned",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "da76c135-89d1-4b24-8770-dbc513b5ed25",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1895.0,
      "y": 6304.680555555556,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "判断变量为空对象{}",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "eec189d4-464b-4bac-a079-b20db2a36750",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": 6224.680555555556,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "判断是否有自身存在的属性，如果存在则不为空对象，如果不存在自身的属性（不包括继承的属性），那么变量为空对象",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "ef11355a-cc94-48ae-8f40-fc44a6695947",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": 6384.680555555556,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "// 判断变量为空\nfunction isEmpty(obj) {\n\n  for(let key in obj) {\n\n      if(obj.hasOwnProperty(key)) {\n\n         return false;\n\n      }\n\n  }\n\n  return true;\n\n}",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "e3c0135b-581a-48ad-b242-0e0e7e0f655e",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1895.0,
      "y": 6624.680555555556,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "判断变量为空数组",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "ac825986-7646-40f3-ba5d-bafa5ac6b650",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": 6544.680555555556,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "判断变量是否为空数组时，首先需要判断变量是否为数组，然后通过数组的length属性确定",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "fd8bc4c0-2206-4fc5-9080-df0601b74481",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": 6704.680555555556,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "Array.isArray(arr) && arr.length === 0",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "c5e4f7a7-34a4-4f2e-aed4-6c29f355ef3d",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1895.0,
      "y": 7024.680555555556,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "判断变量为0或者NaN",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "4d035209-ce92-4f14-bb49-fffad9fcad42",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": 6864.680555555556,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "当一个变量为Number类型时，判空即判断变量是否为0或者NaN，因为NaN与任何值比较都为false，所以我们可以通过取非运算符完成",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "b72f9775-75d1-442c-949d-d1c575498901",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": 7024.680555555556,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "!(Number(num) && num) == true;",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "319255cd-74bf-40f4-aab0-25e28f978466",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2735.0,
      "y": 7024.680555555556,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "​",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "2ac1eb49-2c6c-4651-8ecd-0ced4db795ea",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": 7184.680555555556,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "前提该变量得是Number类型",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "9b4d378b-84d3-443e-add0-14a0daae7cc8",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 1895.0,
      "y": 7664.680555555556,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "!x == true的所有情况",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "541b08ca-3d93-4728-bfe0-ff3e5b6d24cd",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 2315.0,
      "y": 7344.680555555556,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 120,
      "text": "null",
      "color": "5"
    },
    {
      "id": "f954e084-2b42-46e0-918b-f592c3be04c2",
      "type": "text",
